OL,3,CTeachers 'reluctant to use AI for
OL,4,Cpupil learning and assessment'
OL,6,FMost teachers are reluctant to use or
OL,7,Fare not interested in artificial
OL,8,Fintelligence for pupil learning and
OL,9,Fassessment, new research has found.
OL,11,FA study of more than 5,000 teachers by
OL,12,FBCS, The Chartered Institute for IT,
OL,13,Ffound that the majority (64%) are not
OL,14,Fusing AI tools such as ChatGPT
OL,15,Fprofessionally, and 19% are not
OL,16,Finterested in using it in the future.
