OL,6,FA lack of clarity on their schools'
OL,7,Fpolicy around AI also appeared to be
OL,8,Fan issue, with 41% saying their school
OL,9,Fdoes not have an agreed approach to
OL,10,FAI, while 17% said they do not know if
OL,11,Fany such policy exists.
