OL,3,CTeachers 'reluctant to use AI for
OL,4,Cpupil learning and assessment'
OL,6,F"But they need better training and
OL,7,Fguidance to grow in confidence with
OL,8,FAI, to make sure it is used fairly and
OL,9,Fthat it doesn't cause greater
OL,10,Fdisadvantage in the education system."
OL,12,FSarah Hannafin, head of policy for
OL,13,Fschool leaders' union NAHT, said:
OL,14,F"While it is clear that AI has huge
OL,15,Fpotential benefits for schools and
OL,16,Fchildren's learning, it is important
OL,17,Fthat these are harnessed in the right
OL,18,Fway.
