OL,3,CTeachers 'reluctant to use AI for
OL,4,Cpupil learning and assessment'
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, the Government announced
OL,7,Fthat it had asked Ofsted to carry out
OL,8,Fresearch into artificial intelligence
OL,9,Fin education, to investigate how
OL,10,Fschools and further education colleges
OL,11,Fare using AI to support teaching and
OL,12,Flearning, as well as to manage
OL,13,Fadministrative systems and processes.
OL,15,FThe Government said it will use the
OL,16,Fdata collected to understand how AI is
OL,17,Falready being used and to help it
OL,18,Fconsider the technologies potential
OL,19,Fuses and benefits.
